ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectInternational Convention against Doping in Sport
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to accept, on behalf of the Government of Canada, that amendments to Annex I of the INTERNATIONAL CONVENTION AGAINST DOPING IN SPORT be binding on Canada.
